{"tid":33927,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"珠海學院今年收得3xx人","createTime":"2016-12-11T07:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T12:46:06.000Z","uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5b27ceeab9de186124d2d03d53b9dd4872cbf5","tid":33927,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=OBmMLW3ZCeYTmCBe%2FFpp%2B6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=63fd9252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】大專院校學生會主要依靠學生繳交的會費維持營運，若學生不肯交費，學生會又怎樣運作下去呢？本學年搬入屯門新校舍的珠海學院，最新學生會會章規定，本年度新生每個學期需繳交100港元學生會會費，但開學至今幾個月，只有約13%的學生已繳會費，合共有4千多港元，令珠海學生會本年度陷入財政困難，學生會及各屬會活動或受影響。 <br />\n<br />\n珠海學院學生會編輯委員會《海聲》表示，自上學年開始，繳交學費的方式取消了舊有的現金支付方法，並改為以繳費靈(PPS)繳交或提交銀行支票，學生會會費亦只能以PPS繳交，不少學生投訴新繳費方式十分不便，亦有未繳交學生會會費的學生稱，由於學生會會政不透明，令他們減低繳費意欲。 <br />\n<br />\n珠海學院學生會內務副會長鄭詠心對只有少數學生繳交會費感到十分無奈，她指新的繳費安排暫未能提供欠交學生會會費的學生名單，學生會無法有效地向學生追收款項，她呼籲學生盡快繳交會費，以應付學生會及各屬會的活動支出。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每人要比100蚊 有13%既人比左 一共4千幾蚊<br />\n屌你同拆穿人地收得300幾人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9930a91896f1afac0786bad8df104aed06f864","tid":33927,"uid":16885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"當夠5000蚊得384人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93b7325047c69c5c0e04c6e45be46b1ea3a99a4","tid":33927,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:13:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=26234752&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D26234752%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=OBmMLW3ZCeYTmCBe%2FFpp%2B6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=4d27ace4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=26234752&amp;extra=page%3D1</a><br />\n<br />\nsor 原來得百幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無li仔係珠大人呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5282e8f496b38905c9566fed9c8e0662e0b2e711","tid":33927,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:15:33.000Z","msg":"乜呢間學校淨係freshmen要俾人劏會費架咩？"},{"pid":"6bbd41b6fadff7805a5cf7b3425deb9d4d37fd50","tid":33927,"uid":27708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"仲有yr2,3,4<br />\n你點計數<br />\n一百人都俾多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ea43fc6fbcef6e1a0c44287f304d25c4ad8df7","tid":33927,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}